# Fix_Google_Play
# Route these through proxy so services.googleapis.cn returns a global CDN URL,
# and xn--ngstr-lra8j.com (Google global CDN) is reached consistently via proxy.
# See: https://github.com/nicehash/NiceHashQuickMiner/issues/xxx (Google Play "waiting" fix)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,googleapis.cn
DOMAIN,clientservices.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,update.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,fonts.googleapis.com
